{"tid":580639,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"HR撚入 年假問題","createTime":"2018-03-04T16:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T05:02:05.000Z","uid":74293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c02b8e6dfb76488dc73a87299ba2968a0b08a19e","tid":580639,"uid":74293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"想問下離職的時候，剩餘AL11.6日 按照勞工法例/僱傭條例是否應該當作12日計算？<br />\n<br />\n可否請大神幫忙引條文出來？<br />\n<br />\n如果公司拒絕當一日計算，是否觸犯法律？<br />\n<br />\n以下是從某人力資源網站複製出來的：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.carbonik.com/zh-hk/blog/hr-excel-leave\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.carbonik.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fblog%2Fhr-excel-leave&d=v5gXNw8t0g5mCxe%2BPAM8gaNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=4988155e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.carbonik.com/zh-hk/blog/hr-excel-leave</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n須注意，在第一年裡，可享日數須按已入職日數按比例&quot;pro-rata&quot;計算，並且根據《僱傭條例》，每論該年是否潤年，計算比例時其份母必然是365，而不會是366。計算結果中不足一日的部分將被當作一整日。"},{"pid":"09c774579c16a9c1daf2071276c281c7b152184d","tid":580639,"uid":35233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"如果你每年年假數係勞工法例下最低界線（例如第一年7日），就當一日，如果唔係就按實數/公司policy 處理"},{"pid":"62d5491b97fda520f2f2dd467912dda5d619f308","tid":580639,"uid":60000,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:59:35.000Z","msg":"多數11.5 round up <br />\n11.49 round down"},{"pid":"9f09cdb287634619b69348926ef7d253e41cf448","tid":580639,"uid":29212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"想問埋 如果我仲有12AL辭職 公司應該補水要我做夠一個月定係可以俾我離職前扣哂12日AL? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a497879cda57606178ad3dcf1ab09a46c10b7c05","tid":580639,"uid":83748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:12:38.000Z","msg":"正常情況下 離職時公司會將你有嘅年假 計返錢俾你 <br />\n<br />\n按一個叫每日平均工資 x 11.6 <br />\n<br />\n唔會變12 而你qoute嘅情況大多用係一隻叫共同假期年嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n同你個case無關 另一樣野嚟<br />\n<br />\n利伸 幾年勞記經驗"},{"p